            "kind": "heading",
            "text": "How to use it"
          },
          {
            "kind": "steps",
            "steps": [
              {
                "title": "Pick your blob(s)",
                "note": "Which figure(s) feel most like you right now? You can choose more than one, or none — that is also data."
